                          k
                        
                      
                    
                  
                
              
            
          
          )
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \ln(x)=(x-1)\prod _{k=1}^{\infty }\left({\frac {2}{1+{\sqrt[{2^{k}}]{x}}}}\right)}
  Two examples might be:

  
    
      
